*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Report ZPRGSD115_EMAIL_FOR_EXP_NOTICE
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT zprgsd115_email_for_exp_notice.

SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF BLOCK b1 WITH FRAME TITLE TEXT-t01.
  PARAMETERS: p_date TYPE sy-datum.
SELECTION-SCREEN END OF BLOCK b1.

PERFORM f_process_email.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form f_process_email
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM f_process_email .

  DATA: vl_dats TYPE draw-vrldat.

  CLEAR vl_dats.

  IF p_date IS INITIAL.
    vl_dats = sy-datum + 60.
  ELSE.
    vl_dats = p_date + 60.
  ENDIF.


  CALL FUNCTION 'ZFNCSD115_EMAIL_FOR_EXP_NOTICE'
    EXPORTING
      p_vrldat = vl_dats.
ENDFORM.
